org.amv.access.sdk.spi.communication

Interface CommandFactory


  • public interface CommandFactory
    An interface for creating commands which can be used to interact with a connected device.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Command disconnect()
      A command for closing the bluetooth connection on the module side.
      Command lockDoors()
      A command for locking the doors on a vehicle.
      Command sendVehicleStatus()
      A command representing the request to send the current vehicle state.

      • sendVehicleStatus

        A command representing the request to send the current vehicle state.
        Returns:

      • disconnect

        Command disconnect()
        A command for closing the bluetooth connection on the module side.

        This is needed cause e.g. devices with Android version greater or equal to 6 don't close physical connections reliably.

        Returns:
        a command for closing Bluetooth connection.
